snippet.title: The Life Stage: Virtual House (3DO) Space House
snippet.description: This time on "3DO Cribs," we go inside a spacious outer space house that is simply out of this world! Brought to you by "The Life Stage: Virtual House" from Micro Cabin. Captured from original hardware. Footage (mostly loading time) has been edited.
